name: Kiki Chilling Under Moonlight | Kiki's Playground #13
description: Kiki's Playground is a way for new and experienced artists to find inspiration and have a platform to sell their art the same time. Create what inspires you when you think of 'Kiki', no other rules. The cut is 80%/20%, with the artist retaining the majority split. Anyone who is interested will be able to have their submission minted, and I'll take care of the minting costs. Interested artists can register on Twitter at @KikiNFT.  Artist: @Mubblegum
